    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at DXC Technology India. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Senior Software Engineer to strengthen our Delhi-based team.\n\nAbout DXC Technology India:\nDXC Technology India is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Learning & development budget\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Delhi, Delhi, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with DXC Technology India!",
